tables.table_schema: CREATE TABLE trademarks (id INT, name VARCHAR(255), registration_number VARCHAR(50), expiration_date DATE);
CREATE TABLE trademark_owners (owner_id INT, trademark_id INT, owner_name VARCHAR(255), address VARCHAR(255));
CREATE TABLE trademarks (registration_number VARCHAR(255), expiration_date DATE)
CREATE TABLE trademark_owners (owner_name VARCHAR(255), contact_info VARCHAR(255))
CREATE TABLE trademark_details (trademark_id INT, trademark_description TEXT)
CREATE TABLE trademarks (id INT PRIMARY KEY, trademark_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL, registration_number VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL, expiration_date DATE NOT NULL);
CREATE TABLE trademark_owners (id INT PRIMARY KEY, owner_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL, registration_id INT NOT NULL, FOREIGN KEY (registration_id) REFERENCES trademarks(id));
CREATE TABLE trademark_categories (id INT PRIMARY KEY, category_name VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL, description TEXT);
CREATE TABLE trademark_history (id INT PRIMARY KEY, trademark_id INT NOT NULL, event_date DATE NOT NULL, description TEXT, FOREIGN KEY (trademark_id) REFERENCES trademarks(id));
